Supplementary Figure 5 . The binding kinetics of m336, m336-gH, m336-gL and m336-gL-FR to MERS-CoV S1 Single-cycle surface plasmon resonance analyses were carried out to assess binding of m336 variants to MERS-CoV S1. Antibody at five concentrations were injected incrementally in a single cycle onto a CM5 sensor chip immobilized with MERS-CoV S1 protein. The kinetic profiles are shown in each panel.
